<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Defence Career Path</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stream-detail.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="stream-hero">
    <span>Service and Discipline Stream</span>
    <h1>Defence Career Path</h1>
    <p>Defence careers include the Army, Navy, Air Force, Coast Guard, paramilitary forces, and defence technology. This path suits students with discipline, courage, fitness, leadership, and service mindset.</p>
  </header>
  <main class="stream-shell">
    <section class="quick-grid">
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Main Focus</strong>Fitness, discipline, academics, leadership</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Common Exams</strong>NDA, CDS, AFCAT, Agniveer, Coast Guard entries</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Best For</strong>Service, courage, teamwork, responsibility</div>
    </section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Popular Defence Fields</h2>
    <section class="path-grid">
      <div class="path-card active"><h3>Army</h3><p>Land-based operations, leadership, logistics, infantry, engineering, and support roles.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Navy</h3><p>Serve at sea through ships, submarines, aviation, technical, and logistics branches.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Air Force</h3><p>Flying, technical, ground duty, air defence, and administrative roles.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Paramilitary</h3><p>Serve in forces like BSF, CRPF, ITBP, CISF, and SSB.</p></div>
    </section>
    <section class="tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" data-target="courses">Preparation</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="exams">Entrance Exams</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="careers">Careers</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="skills">Skills</button>
    </section>
    <section class="detail-panel">
      <div id="courses" class="tab-panel active"><h2>Preparation Path</h2><ul><li>After 12th, prepare for NDA if eligible.</li><li>After graduation, prepare for CDS, AFCAT, CAPF, or other entries.</li><li>Maintain physical fitness and medical standards from early stages.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="exams" class="tab-panel"><h2>Entrance Exams</h2><ul><li>NDA for Army, Navy, and Air Force after 12th.</li><li>CDS for graduates entering officer training academies.</li><li>AFCAT for Air Force officer entries, plus Agniveer and Coast Guard options.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="careers" class="tab-panel"><h2>Career Options</h2><ul><li>Army Officer, Naval Officer, Air Force Officer, Soldier, Sailor, Airman.</li><li>Technical Officer, Logistics Officer, Pilot, Defence Engineer.</li><li>CAPF Assistant Commandant, Police and security services.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="skills" class="tab-panel"><h2>Skills To Build</h2><ul><li>Physical fitness, discipline, decision-making, and teamwork.</li><li>General knowledge, maths, English, and reasoning.</li><li>Leadership, confidence, and communication for interviews and SSB.</li></ul></div>
    </section>
    <section class="planner"><h2>Student Checklist</h2><label><input type="checkbox"> Start a daily fitness routine.</label><label><input type="checkbox"> Track NDA/CDS/AFCAT eligibility and age limits.</label><label><input type="checkbox"> Practice current affairs, reasoning, and English.</label></section>
    <div class="back-row"><a class="action-link" href="career.jsp">Back to Career Streams</a></div>
  </main>
  <script src="stream-detail.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
